content:
Dependency Injection
==

> 依赖注入是控制反转(`Inversion of Control`)的一种实现方式

- 不使用控制反转
```js
class Person {
    eat() {
        const dinner = new Dinner('法国菜');
        console.log('开饭啦！，今晚自己做：', dinner.name);
    }
}

class Dinner {
    constructor(name) {
        this.name = name;
    }
}
```

- 使用控制反转

```js
class Person {
    eat(dinner) {
        console.log('开饭啦！，今晚有大厨给我做：', dinner.name);
    }
}
```
